# Artometrics — global rules

- **Imports:** Use the `@/` alias for the project root (e.g. `@/components/SiteHeader`, `@/lib/content`, `@/constants/Colors`). Match existing patterns in this repo.
- **Scope:** Keep changes minimal and localized. No drive-by refactors or unrelated files.
- **Dependencies:** Do not add packages or features not requested; only use what appears in `package.json` unless the user explicitly asks to add one.
- **Stack:** Expo + Expo Router only — do not reintroduce Astro.
- **Content:** Edit markdown under `src/content/`; run `npm run content` (or rely on prestart/prebuild) so `src/generated/` stays in sync.
- **Layouts:** Site chrome lives in `app/(site)/_layout.tsx` (`SiteHeader` + `SiteFooter`).
- **Branding:** Public-facing copy, legal pages, and project docs should use **Artometrics** — not Lexington/Hemingway theme demo text.
- **Publisher docs:** Product and contributor documentation live in the root `README.md` and `AGENTS.md`.
